[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has a 7-card \S suit but he is too strong to open with a preemptive bid. 
So he opens 1\S instead.

NORTH should respond 2\C, and SOUTH can do nothing but rebid the \S suit.

NORTH thinks there should be game and bids 4\S}

